{"tid":875991,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"紐時：中國監聽特朗普iPhone　中國外交部：憂竊聽可改用華為","createTime":"2018-10-25T09:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-25T13:03:02.000Z","uid":39464,"like":230,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":60,"replies":[{"pid":"9ea87fc9f8c1a6c2494a578e7efced6833ac1d51","tid":875991,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181025/s00005/a89f10edd11493940652c463cacca78c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181025%2Fs00005%2Fa89f10edd11493940652c463cacca78c.jpg&h=1ccf4bb1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國《紐約時報》報道，中國和俄羅斯情報部門一直監聽美國總統特朗普的個人蘋果iPhone。在北京，外交部發言人華春瑩回應指，感覺美方有些人在「不遺餘力地角逐奧斯卡最佳劇本獎」，又建議「如果很擔心蘋果手機被竊聽的話，可以改用華為手機」。<br />\n<br />\n《紐約時報》周三（24日）引述多位匿名現任及前白宮官員稱，特朗普用自己的iPhone打電話給朋友閒聊時，中國的間諜「經常監聽」，特朗普的助理也多次警告他用個人手機打電話不安全，因為俄羅斯間諜也會定期監聽這些電話。<br />\n<br />\n今日下午，有美國有線新聞網絡（CNN）的記者，在北京舉行的外交部例行記者會上向華春瑩提問。華春瑩回應：「看這個報道，感覺現在美方有些人真是在不遺餘力地角逐奧斯卡最佳劇本獎」。華春瑩說完不禁一笑。<br />\n<br />\n華春瑩又提出三點：「第一，《紐約時報》應該知道，發表類似報道只會多一個《紐約時報》在做fake news（假新聞）的證據。第二，如果很擔心蘋果手機被竊聽的話，可以改用華為手機，第三，如果還覺得不放心，為了絕對安全起見，可以停止使用任何現代通訊設備，斷絕與外界的所有聯繫。」<br />\n<br />\n特朗普今年8月簽署國防授權法，禁止美國政府和政府承包商使用華為和中興通訊的部分技術。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181025/s00005/1540456929673\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181025%2Fs00005%2F1540456929673&d=yXBy8Gr5BmAXxHuzw1Mkgozu7PIJYhBZqlGrkalTKs4%3D&h=dd2539b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181025%2Fs00005%2F1540456929673&h=c78b662f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181025/s00005/1540456929673</a>"},{"pid":"47bde02ba5e011a6d256410b9339eede76e38c62","tid":875991,"uid":70786,"like":318,"dislike":0,"score":318,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:24:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">感覺美方有些人在「不遺餘力地角逐奧斯卡最佳劇本獎」</span><br />\n<br />\n華春蠅你一定拎最佳女配角同演技獎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"235b1dbefe1ea8e01c647ea83dc912776ff9b9d2","tid":875991,"uid":32782,"like":234,"dislike":3,"score":231,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:25:19.000Z","msg":"咁撚幽默嘅喂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e5039b0b5e064c6a5ce864cfe3ad7a5b47b3cfd","tid":875991,"uid":29093,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:25:44.000Z","msg":"apple watch錄音單野呢 ?"},{"pid":"9be64c443e15f3c2c15287c37ca056a99b037f00","tid":875991,"uid":43041,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:26:08.000Z","msg":"咁撚串<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d434bc17e9f22b91e7acc1373774ecefeff8ddf","tid":875991,"uid":57787,"like":194,"dislike":2,"score":192,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:26:18.000Z","msg":"佢無講錯，用華為即係開心share，咁就唔叫竊聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f4e5bb2a6c0a00e72e7a7e603124e4c949a7d4","tid":875991,"uid":156652,"like":28,"dislike":3,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:26:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f9x9viu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff9x9viu.jpg&h=3f0b48c7&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa4e15181db6c72b9e4c0b4e9e973872b9331f48","tid":875991,"uid":20241,"like":75,"dislike":2,"score":73,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-25T09:26:50.000Z","msg":"第一，《紐約時報》應該知道，發表類似報道只會多一個《紐約時報》在做fake news（假新聞）的證據。第二，如果很擔心蘋果手機被竊聽的話，可以改用華為手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n佢又幾貼地 有啲白宮發言人風格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f3378db3399e78fc2124c42b5de9eec634e31c","tid":875991,"uid":140538,"like":5,"dislike":15,"score":-10,"quote":{"pid":"235b1dbefe1ea8e01